title: Europa Universalis IV 1.7.0 Multiplayer Steam Fix
description:
First crack I uploaded was a failture; because of new launcher shit.

But I found this crack and turns out this works!  

1. Install EU4
2. Install patch 1.6.2
3. Install patch 1.6.2 to 1.7.0
4. Copy the files in 3DM Crack to your game folder.
5. Copy the files in Steam Fix to your game folder.
6. Run Steam and login.
7. Run the game and play with your friends!
